%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20urge%20my%20colleagues%20in%20the%20BJP%20to%20prioritise%20transformation%20of%20the%20mindset.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20they%20demonstrate%20genuine%20respect%20for%20women%20by%20aligning%20their%20actions%20with%20their%20words.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20that%20they%20take%20appropriate%20action%20against%20individuals%20who%20are%20harming%20women%20and%20showing%20disrespect%20towards%20women.%20The%20golden%20girls%20of%20the%20country%20who%20got%20us%20medals%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20and%20they%20were%20in%20Jantar%20Mantar%20but%20the%20perpetrator%20sits%20here%20today%20%E2%80%93%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20who%20has%20not%20been%20brought%20to%20book%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20if%20you%20are%20really%20interested%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20women%20towards%20betterment%20and%20progress%20then%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20take%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Dastidar%E2%80%99s%20party%20colleague%20TMC%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20also%20asked%20if%20the%20BJP%20is%20serious%20about%20the%20empowerment%20of%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20struggles%20of%20women%20are%20not%20because%20of%20women%20but%20because%20of%20men%20and%20their%20outlook%20of%20women.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20waste%20my%20time%20on%20a%20former%20wrestling%20chief%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20alluding%20to%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20irony%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20presence%20during%20the%20debate%20was%20also%20raised%20by%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20MP%20Harsimrat%20Kaur%20Badal%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edelimitation%20and%20census%20clause%20tied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20legislation%2C%20Badal%20said%20that%20before%20an%20election%2C%20every%20political%20party%20comes%20to%20woo%20women%20voters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20aren%E2%80%99t%20crimes%20against%20women%20ever%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%3F%20In%20the%20last%20five%20years%20crimes%20against%20women%20have%20increased%20by%2026%25.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20that%20when%20women%20in%20Manipur%20are%20harassed%2C%20the%20government%20does%20not%20open%20its%20mouth%20for%20three%20months.%20And%20only%20breaks%20its%20silence%20after%20a%20no-confidence%20motion.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20a%20minister%20is%20accused%20of%20sexual%20assault%20but%20enjoys%20a%20cabinet%20rank%20status.%20Women%20wrestlers%20who%20have%20won%20medals%20for%20our%20country%20are%20waiting%20for%20months%20but%20the%20Baahubali%20is%20still%20sitting%20here.%20306%20MPs%20%5Bin%20both%20houses%5D%20have%20cases%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F40-sitting-mps-have-criminal-cases-25-serious-criminal-cases-adr-8936699%2F%5C%22%3Erape%20and%20sexual%20assault%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%A6%20Is%20this%20Beti%20Bachao%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbrij-bhushan-sharan-singh-profile%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esix%20Lok%20Sabha%20victories%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Singh%20has%20won%20five%20times%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20and%20once%20(in%202009)%20on%20an%20SP%20ticket.%20He%20won%20the%20first%20two%20elections%20in%201991%20and%201999%20from%20the%20Gonda%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20In%20the%202004%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20gave%20him%20a%20ticket%20from%20Balrampur%20and%20nominated%20Ghanshyam%20Shukla%20from%20Gonda.%20Shukla%20died%20in%20a%20road%