20a%20%26quot%3Bcolossal%20failure%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E'But%20there%20was%20nobody%20else%20and%20I%20did%20it...%20and%20it%20was%20successful.%20Many%20things%20happen%20in%20life%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-updates-isro-satisfied-with-data-isro-chief-s-somanath-discusses-chandrayaan-3-challenges-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Must%20Have%20Permanent%20Habitat%20On%20Moon%20And%20Mars%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20To%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20boss%2C%20with%20a%20smile%20on%20his%20face%2C%20said%20that%20though%20he%20had%20been%20criticised%20and%20his%20ability%20questioned%2C%20he%20had%20taught%20himself%20to%20rise%20above%20the%20%26quot%3Bsilly%20words...%20silly%20acts%26quot%3B%20of%20some%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'...you%20are%20not%20a%20suitable%20person%20(for%20this%20role)'...%20I%20hear%20all%20this%20criticism%20but%20you%20have%20to%20raise%20yourself%20above%20these%20silly%20things.%20Once%20you%20reach%20that%20point%20(of%20self-confidence)%20you%20can%20look%20at%20people%20like%20this%20and%20smile.%20Their%20silly%20acts%20can%20be%20ignored.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwork-of-a-generation-isro-chief-on-chandrayaan-3s-moon-landing-4323123%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWork%20Of%20A%20Generation%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20On%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Moon%20Landing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20to%20do%20that%3F%20You%20go%20through%20a%20process...%20learn%20how%20to%20develop%20your%20self-confidence.%20And%20once%20you%20do%20that%20then%20you%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20these%20silly%20people%20and%20their%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20who%20made%20Indi