2%80%94%20have%20copied%20TikTok's%20tech.%20But%20neither%20Reels%20nor%20Shorts%20can%20replicate%20the%20culture%3A%20A%20scroll%20through%20Instagram%20will%20surface%20many%20repurposed%20TikToks%20or%20content%20inspired%20by%20a%20TikTok%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20creators%20continue%20churning%20out%20original%20content%2C%20a%20feat%20at%20a%20time%20when%20engagement%20on%20social%20apps%20is%20shifting%20away%20from%20public%20posting%20to%20more%20private%20conversations%20in%20DMs%20and%20group%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvertising%20keeps%20the%20wheel%20spinning%2C%20commerce%20accelerates%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221838%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20of%20TikTok%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650de83b23ce9d0019089bf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22970%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20Intelligence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20because%20TikTok%20builds%20a%20shop%2C%20doesn't%20mean%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20will%20come.%20No%20social%20app%20has%20been%20able%20to%20conquer%20US%20e-commerce%2C%20and%20the%20200%2C000%20TikTok%20Shop%20merchants%20represent%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20TikTok's%20reported%205%20million%20US%20business%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20marketplace%2C%20full%20of%20deeply%20discounted%20and%20copycat%20goods%2C%20is%20a%20jarring%20departure%20from%20the%20personalized%2C%20entertaining%20experience%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20app%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20does%20have%20several%20things%20working%20in%20its%20favor%3A%20It%20caters%20to%20a%20young%20audience%2C%20whose%20shopping%20habits%20and%20retailer%20loyalties%20are%20still%20forming.%20It%20has%20a%20roadmap%20and%20deep%20resources%20in%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%2C%20which%20can%20afford%20the%20%24500%20million%20loss%20TikTok%20Shop%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%