ew%20members.%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Biggs%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20stop%20was%20Nassau%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthe-bahamas-things-to-never-do-according-to-local-photos-2022-7%23contrary-to-popular-belief-there-are-places-worth-visiting-besides-new-providence-and-paradise-island-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Bahamas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20beach%20was%20hot%20and%20crowded%2C%20and%20loud%20music%20made%20the%20whole%20scene%20overwhelming.%20I%20probably%20would%20have%20preferred%20booking%20an%20excursion%2C%20which%20is%20a%20paid%20experience%20like%20snorkeling%20or%20hiking%20that's%20facilitated%20by%20Royal%20Caribbean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%20the%20ship%20docked%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fperfect-day-cococay-private-bahamian-island-tour-photos-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECocoCay%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20private%20island%20owned%20by%20Admiral%20Cruises%2C%20which%20has%20been%20owned%20by%20Royal%20Caribbean%20since%201988.%20Admiral%20Cruises%20leased%20the%20island%20until%202050%20in%201985%2C%20and%20it%20will%20probably%20be%20renewed%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalcaribbeanblog.com%2F2021%2F12%2F13%2Fcomparing-royal-caribbeans-private-islands-cococay-labadee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoyal%20Caribbean%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20island%20got%20a%20%24250%20million%20renovation.%20Now%20Coco%20Cay%20has%20a%20water%20park%20with%2013%20slides%2C%20an%20exclusive%20beach%20club%20and%20two%20pools%2C%20a%20wave%20pool%20and%20a%20freshwater%20pool%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20the%20region's%20largest.%20The%20only%20people%20who%20live%20on%20the%20island%20full%20time%20are%20employees%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalcaribbeanblog.com%2Fperfect-day-cococay-tips-tricks-secrets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoyal%20Caribbean%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays.%20Can%20you%20talk%20about%20a%20dream%20job%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20shoreline%20along%20South%20Beach%20on%20Coco%20Cay%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65035c5d2a72d60019d5465e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECocoCay%20provided%20the%20serene%20tropical%20destination%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3Cp%3EHaley%20Tenore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20liked%20CocoCay.%20It%20was%20just%20as%20hot%20and%20humid%20as%20Nassau%2C%20but%20we%20could%20hop%20on%20trams%20that%20shuttled%20people%20around%20the%20island%20to%20avoid%20the%20crowds.%20There%20were%20beaches%20with%20soft%20white%20sand%20and%20crystal%20clear%20turquoise%20waters.%20We%20disembarked%20earlier%20than%20most%20passengers%2C%20so%20we%20got%20to%20enjoy%20the%20beach%20before%20the%20crowds%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enjoyed%20the%20beach%20so%20much%20that%20I%20stayed%20in%20the%20ocean%20all%20morning.%20I%20wish%20we%20had%20more%20time%20on%20the%20island%2C%20but%20we%20had%20to%20be%20back%20on%20board%20by%202%20p.m.%20to%20sail%20back%20to%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221243%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabin%20hallways%20on%20the%20Royal%20Caribbean%20Vision%20of%20the%20Seas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65035a6f2a72d60019d54351%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20unnerved%20by%20how%20long%20the%20hallways%20outside%20the%20ship's%20cabins%20were.%3Cp%3EHaley%20Tenore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20had%20several%20dining%20options%2C%20including%20a%20buffet%2C%20a%20dining%20room%2C%20room%20service%2C%20and%20a%20Ben%20and%20Jerry's%20kiosk%20that%20also%20served%20Starbucks%20coffee.%20Overall%2C%20I%20was%20pleased%20with%20everything%20I%20ate.%20But%20I%20did%20also%20notice%20that%20the%20portions%20were%20usually%20on%20the%20smaller%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20food%20highlights%20from%20my%20trip%20include%20the%20New%20York%20Strip%20Steak%20and%20the%20Royal%20Cheesecake%2C%20both%20of%20which%20I%20got%20from%20the%20main%20dining%20room%2C%20and%20some%20chicken%20wings%20I%20got%20as%20room%20service%20on%20the%20last%20night%20of%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalcaribbean.com%2Fbooked%2Fbeverage-packages%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefreshment%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20did%20not%20include%20alcohol%20%E2%80%94%20I%20learned%20this%20the%20hard%20way%20after%20being%20charged%20%2415%20for%20a%20mimosa.%20There%20were%20bars%20on%20almost%20every%20deck%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20try%20lots%20of%20different%20mocktails.%20My%20favorite%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20virgin%20strawberry%20daiquiri.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20complaint%20was%20that%20the%20ship%20was%20packed.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-cruise-like-reality-vs-expectation-disappointing-photos-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrowding%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20an%20issue%20throughout%20the%20entire%20vessel.%20Oftentimes%20I%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20sit.%20I'd%20have%20to%20fight%20through%20hordes%20of%20people%20to%20get%20food%20at%20the%20buffet%2C%20and%20people%20would%20cram%20the%20elevators%20to%20their%20very%20limits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221243%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sunset%20on%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20Vision%20of%20the%20Seas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650357cb2a72d60019d54003%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20the%20Windjammer%20buffet%20wasn't%20packed%20with%20people%20it%20was%20a%20nice%20place%20to%20watch%20the%20sun%20set.%3Cp%3EHaley%20Tenore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20shocked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthings-i-dont-pay-extra-for-cruises-save-money-2023-6%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20everything%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20bought%20a%20packet%20of%20peach%20rings%20from%20the%20gift%20shop%20one%20day%20because%20I%20was%20hungry%20between%20mealtimes%20at%20the%20buffet.%20They%20had%20no%20price%20tag%2C%20but%20I%20figured%20they'd%20be%20no%20more%20than%20%245.%20It%20turns%20out%20they%20were%20%2415.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20a%20little%20more%20than%20I%20hoped%20to%2C%20but%20at%20least%20I%20was%20rarely%20bored.%20There%20were%20several%20ways%20to%20stay%20entertained%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20including%20shows%2C%20games%2C%20and%20my%20favorite%3A%20the%20two%20pools.%20The%20pools%20got%20crowded%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20ship%2C%20however%2C%20and%20boat's%20swaying%20meant%20led%20to%20lots%20of%20awkward%20moments%20bumping%20into%20strangers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20Nassau%20from%20the%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65035ddb2a72d60019d54881%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20we%20docked%20in%20Nassau%2C%20we%20got%20a%20view%20of%20what%20looked%20like%20the%20Atlantis%20Paradise%20Island%20Bahamas%20resort.%3Cp%3EHaley%20Tenore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20the%20trip%20was%20the%20crew%2C%20who%20were%20all%20nice%20and%20helpful.%20Royal%20Caribbean%20employs%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20and%20I%20enjoyed%20be%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20such%20diversity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20write%20off%20going%20on%20another%20cruise%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I%20prefer%20planning%20my%20own%20trips.%20With%20this%20cruise%2C%20everything%20was%20pre-planned%20%E2%80%94%20right%20down%20to%20the%20times%20I%20was%20able%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20going%20to%20a%20new%20city%2C%20state%2C%20or%20country%2C%20I%20like%20to%20be%20able%20to%20plan%20where%20I'm%20gonna%20go%2C%20how%20long%20I'm%20going%20to%20spend%20there%2C%20how%20much%20money%20I%20will%20spend%2C%20and%20when%20I'm%20going%20to%20need%20downtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20cruise%2C%20or%20work%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%2C%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20from%20a%20non-work%20email%20at%20htenore%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-cruise-ship-vision-bahamas-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695645460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65035f312a72d60019d54ae0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-cruise-ship-vision-bahamas-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20sailed%20on%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20Vision%20of%20the%20Seas%20on%20my%20first%20cruise%20vacation%20despite%20some%20initial%20hesitancy%20toward%20cruising.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htenore%40insider.com%20(Haley%20Tenore)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-cruise-ship-vision-bahamas-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20deserves%20big%20zero%20for%20way%20they%20ruled%20Rajasthan%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695645344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103935512%2Cimgsize-976432.cms%22%2C%22originID%2