g%20them%20for%20tea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20them%20to%20dhabas.%20Treat%20them%20well%20and%20ensure%20no%20negative%20news%20comes%20out%20against%20us.%20There%20should%20be%20positive%20news%20about%20us.%20Protect%20your%20own%20booths%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bawankule%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20declared%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20several%20notable%20achievements%20to%20its%20credit%20but%20that%20these%20were%20being%20obscured%20by%20journalists%20who%20%26quot%3Binsist%20on%20publishing%20whatever%20wrong%20news%20they%20have%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20did%20not%20name%20journalists%20but%20referred%20to%20%26quot%3Bthose%20from%20electronic%20media%20or%20print%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Bawankule's%20comment%20provoked%20a%20furious%20response%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20has%20accused%20him%20and%20the%20BJP%20of%20threatening%20journalists%20to%20manipulate%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20social%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20has%20led%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20biting%20response%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20all%20journalists%20have%20sold%20out...%20do%20you%20think%20journalists%20accept%20crumbs%3F%20I%20can%20understand%20the%20restlessness%20of%20your%20leaders...%20both%20at%20top%20level%20and%20local...%20as%20they%20could%20not%20suppress%20the%20voice%20of%20dissent!%20But%20now%20you%20have%20started%20directly%20making%20offers%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Wadettiwar%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20offer%20%26quot%3Bcrumbs%26quot%3B%20to%20voters%20before%20next%20year's%20election%2C%20in%20which%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20bidding%20for%20an%20unprecedented%20third%20consecutive%20term.%20The%20Congress'%20state%20boss%20has%20ripped%20into%20the%20BJP%20for%20making%20journalists%20look%20%26quot%3Bcheap%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20devaluation%20of%20the%20media%20fraternity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20raged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20ally%20NCP%20has%20also%20responded%3B%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20continuing%20to%20refuse%20dissent%20in%20what%20PM%20Modi's%20government%20has%20hailed%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mother%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNewspapers%20work%20as%20the%20opposition%20in%20a%20democracy...%20but%20the%20BJP%20state%20president%20is%20giving%20lessons%20on%20how%20to%20muzzle%20media.%20It%20is%20a%20serious%20matter%20and%20condemnable%20action.%20It%20is%20the%20BJP's%20policy%20to%20not%20let%20journalists%20function%20smoothly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBJP%20should%20admit%20it%20does%20not%20accept%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20faced%20with%20heavy%20(and%20growing)%20criticism%2C%20Mr%20Bawankule%20has%20said%20his%20comments%20were%20misunderstood.%20%26quot%3BJournalists%20are%20also%20voters.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20if%20you%20(BJP%20workers)%20do%20not%20meet...%20talk%20to%20them...%20or%20seek%20their%20opinion.%20I%20gave%20this%20kind%20of%20advice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20news%20is%20negative%20tomorrow...%20we%20(the%20BJP)%20don't%20have%20an%20opinion.%20It%20is%20your%20(journalists')%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20has%20also%20been%20backed%20by%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20who%20played%20down%20the%20import%20of%20the%20comments.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20need%20to%20interpret%20in%20any%20other%20way.%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20you%20are%20talking%20to%20your%20party%20works%2C%20certain%20things%20are%20said%20in%20a%20lighter%20vein.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EControversy%20over%20the%20comments%20come%20after%20the%20BJP%20slammed%20INDIA%20for%20boycotting%2014%