wood%2Fnews%2Ffardeen-khan-pens-an-emotional-note-on-dad-feroz-khans-84th-birth-anniversary%2Farticleshow%2F103931812.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ugly%20Fans%20and%20Honourable%20Sportspersons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHate%20holds%20dominion%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%20In%20a%20brilliant%20essay%2C%20Priya%20Ramani%20has%20diagnosed%20us%20%E2%80%93%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20that%20is%20Bharat%20%E2%80%93%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fpriya-ramani-im-sorry-inform-your-heart-diseased-8922256%2F%5C%22%3Ehaving%20the%20most%20diseased%20hearts%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pumped%20as%20we%20are%20with%20hate%20and%20prejudice.%20This%20pervasive%2C%20hate-fuelled%20myocardial%20infarction%20is%20triggered%20on%20hearing%20church%20bells%20or%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eazaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Islamic%20prayer%20call)%20or%20seeing%20someone%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%20on%20a%20horse%20or%20sporting%20a%20moustache%2C%20or%20listening%20to%20feminists%20talk%20about%20criminalising%20marital%20rape%3B%20the%20very%20mention%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98M%E2%80%99%20word%20causes%20heartburn.%20Priya%20has%20nailed%20it!%20In%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20this%20life-threatening%20affliction%20has%20poisoned%20every%20segment%20of%20society%2C%20even%20sports%20fans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEtymologically%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cfan%E2%80%9D%20has%20a%20less%20than%20honourable%20lineage.%20It%20springs%20from%20the%20ugly%20term%20%E2%80%9Cfanaticism%E2%80%9D%20that%20connotes%20an%20obsessive%2C%20noxious%20zeal.%20Delving%20deeper%20I%20found%20its%20genesis%20in%20the%20Latin%20word%20%3Cem%3Efanaticus%3C%2Fem%3E%20meaning%20%E2%80%9Cinsanely%20inspired%E2%80%9D.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20fan%20is%20the%20meanest%2C%20most%20dysfunctional%20follower%20of%20the%20game%2C%20a%20vicious%20loser%20who%20turns%20against%20his%20own%20team%20when%20it%20loses.%20Even%20worse%2C%20he%20has%20brought%20bigotry%20into%20the%20mix%2C%20evaluating%20sportspersons%20by%20the%20colour%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20and%20God%20help%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20belong!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAllow%20me%20a%20disclaimer%20at%20this%20point%3A%20as%20a%20sports%20buff%2C%20I%20belong%20to%20an%20era%2C%20nearly%20extinct%2C%20of%20sports%20fans%20who%20loved%20the%20game%20for%20its%20own%20sake.%20Those%20fans%20share%20nothing%20in%20common%20with%20today%E2%80%99s%20fanatics%20who%20masquerade%20as%20sports%20devotees%20but%20are%20small-minded%20racists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20a%20gentler%2C%20more%20civilised%20time%20when%20cricketers%20with%20Muslim%20names%20like%20Mansur%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi%20and%20Salim%20Durani%20were%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20heroes%20and%20the%20stuff%20of%20young%20girls%E2%80%99%20dreams.%20At%20every%20cricket%20stadium%20around%20the%20country%2C%20whenever%20Durani%20came%20out%20to%20bat%2C%20the%20crowd%20would%20erupt%2C%20chanting%20non-stop%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20sixer!%20We%20want%20sixer!%E2%80%9D%20And%20the%20gentle%2C%20charismatic%20Pathan%20rarely%20let%20them%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-indian-is-india-and-other-considerations%5C%22%3EHow%20Indian%20Is%20India%2C%20and%20Other%20Considerations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20stirring%20illustration%20of%20the%20spirit%20of%20sport%20was%20demonstrated%20at%20the%20Chepauk%20stadium%20in%20Chennai%20during%20the%20first%20Test%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%201999.%20In%20a%20gripping%20encounter%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20heroic%20century%20in%20the%20fourth%20innings%20by%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Pakistan%20prevailed%20by%20a%20mere%2012%20runs.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20all%20of%20India%20was%20gutted%20by%20this%20loss%20to%20our%20arch-rivals%2C%20the%20Chennai%20cricket%20fans%20embraced%20our%20common%20shared%20humanity%20by%20giving%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20a%20standing%20ovation%20as%20they%20took%20a%20victory%20lap%2C%20giving%20the%20world%20an%20object%20lesson%20in%20sportsmanship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%20gone!%20India%20is%20no%20longer%20what%20it%20was.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20India%20that%20speaks%20for%20all%20Indians%20but%20a%20divided%20Bharat%20of%20bigoted%20racists%2C%20primitive%20in%20their%20thinking.%20Our%20religious%20identity%20defines%20and%20influences%20our%20thoughts%20and%20actions%2C%20and%20sadly%2C%20it%20is%20a%20religiosity%20that%20is%20not%20tolerant%20and%20caring%20but%20the%20wellspring%20of%20hate%20and%20chauvinism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20World%20Cup%20triumphs%20of%201983%20and%202011%20united%20the%20nation%20in%20joyousness%2C%20that%20spontaneous%20exultation%20was%20missing%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20victory.%20This%20time%20the%20rejoicing%20was%20muted%20and%20there%20were%20no%20banner%20headlines%20lauding%20Mohammed%20Siraj%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20performance.%20Instead%2C%20there%20was%20crass%20and%20shocking%20social%20media%20vulgarity%2C%20denigrating%20what%20he%20had%20achieved.%20The%20obscenest%20was%20the%20image%20of%20an%20exultant%20Siraj%20alongside%20another%20image%20of%20men%20in%20skullcaps%20throwing%20stones%20captioned%20%E2%80%9CSiraj%E2%80%99s%20net%20practice%E2%80%9D.%20As%20a%20nation%2C%20we%20need%20to%20bow%20our%20heads%20in%20shame%20for%20the%20vermin%20in%20our%20midst!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThankfully%2C%20our%20sportspersons%20%E2%80%93%20at%20least%20some%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20have%20spoken%20up%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20confronted%20these%20malevolent%20trolls%20head-on.%20While%20the%20Tendulkars%2C%20the%20Gavaskars%20and%20the%20Shastris%20of%20the%20world%20have%20used%20their%20demigod%20status%20wholly%20to%20embellish%20their%20coffers%2C%20there%20are%20exceptional%20human%20beings%20who%20have%20harnessed%20their%20celebrity%20power%20to%20protest%20injustice%2C%20even%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20personally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVirat%20Kohli%20is%20not%20just%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20batsmen%20this%20country%20has%20produced%20but%20also%20a%20marvellous%20human%20being.%20About%20his%20cricketing%20genius%2C%20suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20while%20Sachin%20is%20ahead%20in%20run%20accumulation%2C%20Virat%20has%20won%20many%20more%20games%20for%20India%20than%20Sachin.%20This%20is%20because%20they%20have%20approached%20the%20game%20differently%20%E2%80%93%20Sachin%20played%20for%20personal%20records%20whereas%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20single-minded%20focus%20was%20on%20winning%20for%20India.%20But%20what%20makes%20Virat%20a%20true%20hero%20is%20his%20sheer%20courage%2C%20humaneness%20and%20unflinching%20support%20for%20his%20men.%20His%20strong%20moral%20compass%20and%20willingness%20to%20take%20personal%20risks%20to%20protect%20the%20values%20he%20holds%20dear%2C%20is%20what%20sets%20him%20apart.%20One%20can%20never%20forget%20his%20sterling%20defence%20of%20his%20beleaguered%20teammate%20after%20our%20T20%20World%20Cup%20defeat%20to%20Pakistan%20in%202021.%20The%20trolls%20went%20ballistic%2C%20directing%20their%20fusillade%20of%20vilest%20abuse%20and%20threats%20at%20the%20only%20Muslim%20in%20the%20team%2C%20Mohammad%20Shami.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20impassioned%20speech%2C%20Kohli%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20Shami%2C%20not%20only%20lashing%20out%20at%20the%20cowardly%20trolls%20who%20use%20the%20anonymity%20of%20social%20media%20to%20besmirch%20hard-earned%20reputations%2C%20but%20launching%20a%20frontal%20assault%20on%20communalism%20which%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20condemnation%20of%20our%20ruler%20and%20his%20ilk.%20His%20soul-stirring%20words%20bear%20repeating%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20me%2C%20attacking%20someone%20over%20their%20religion%20is%20the%20most%20pathetic%20thing%20that%20a%20human%20being%20can%20do.%20I%20have%20never%20ever%20even%20dreamt%20of%20discriminating%20against%20anyone%20over%20their%20religion%E2%80%A6.%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20reason%20why%20we%20are%20playing%20on%20the%20field%20and%20not%20some%20bunch%20of%20spineless%20people%20on%20social%20media%E2%80%A6.%20who%20hide%20behind%20their%20identities%20and%20go%20after%20people%2C%20making%20fun%20of%20people%20and%20that%20has%20become%20social%20entertainment%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%20which%20is%20so%20unfortunate%20and%20so%20sad%20to%20see.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBravo!%20Kohli%20paid%20a%20price%20for%20his%20principled%20stand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Frohit-sharma-replaces-virat-kohli-as-odi-skipper%2Farticle37900409.ece%5C%22%3Elosing%20the%20ODI%20captaincy%20and%20later%20the%20Test%20captaincy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-has-exposed-the-real-face-of-the-bjp-beyond-pr-charm-offensives-studied-silences%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20Has%20Exposed%20the%20Real%20Face%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Beyond%20PR%20Charm%20Offensives%2C%20Studied%20Silences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20Olympic%20and%20world%20champion%2C%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20is%20not%20just%20an%20extraordinary%20javelin-thrower%20but%20an%20extraordinary%20human%20being%20who%20has%20stood%20up%20against%20bigoted%20nationalism%20and%20patriarchy.%20In%20a%20remarkable%20exhibition%20of%20sportsmanship%20and%20decency%20following%20his%20memorable%20Olympic%20gold%20medal%20win%2C%20he%20confronted%20the%20trolls%20for%20unfairly%20targeting%20his%20Pakistani%20counterpart%20Arshad%20Nadeem%2C%20demanding%20that%20they%20not%20use%20his%20name%20to%20further%20their%20%E2%80%9Cdirty%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%20On%20winning%20gold%20at%20the%20recent%20World%20Athletic%20Championship%2C%20he%20further%20infuriated%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhakts%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20inviting%20his%20Pakistani%20mate%20Nadeem%20to%20stand%20next%20to%20him%20as%20he%20held%20the%20tricolour%20that%20enveloped%20them%20both.%20Mind%20you%2C%20Neeraj%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20few%20active%20sportspersons%20who%20spoke%20up%20for%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20protesting%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20age%20of%20racism%2C%20crassness%20and%20bad%20behaviour%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field%2C%20one%20desperately%20looks%20for%20increasingly%20rare%20acts%20of%20decency%20and%20sportsmanship.%20Let%20me%20conclude%20with%20one%20such%20deed%20that%20should%20make%20us%20all%20proud%20to%20be%20Indian%20(or%20Bharati).%20At%20the%20US%20Open%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%2043-year-old%20Rohan%20Bopanna%20reminded%20the%20world%20that%20gracious%20sportsmanship%20was%20more%20important%20than%20winning%20at%20any%20cost.%20In%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20doubles%20final%2C%20trailing%202-4%20in%20the%20deciding%20third%20set%2C%20with%20Bopanna%E2%80%99s%20partner%20Matthew%20Ebden%20serving%2C%20a%20forehand%20winner%20by%20Ebden%20made%20the%20game%20score%2030-0%20in%20their%20favour%2C%20at%20which%20point%20Bopanna%20informed%20the%20chair%20umpire%20that%20Ebden%E2%80%99s%20serve%20had%20grazed%20his%20arm.%20The%20umpire%20initially%20overruled%20his%20objection%2C%20but%20Bopanna%20insisted%20and%20ensured%20that%20she%20gave%20the%20point%20to%20his%20opponents.%20Bopanna%20lost%20the%20match%20but%20won%20hearts%20and%20received%20the%20biggest%20applause%20at%20the%20prize%20distribution%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20think%20that%20Rohan%20Bopanna%20represents%20who%20we%20are%20as%20a%20people%3B%20that%20the%20Ramesh%20Bidhuris%20and%20their%20masters%20are%20%3Cem%3Ea%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Eb%3C%2Fem%3Eharathiya%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(not%20Indian)%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eaberrations%20who%20will%20fade%20away%20in%202024%20when%20decency%20and%20democracy%20once%20again%20prevail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695638743000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fugly-fans-and-honourable-sportspersons%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20age%20of%20racism%2C%20crassness%20and%20bad%20behaviour%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field%2C%20one%20desperately%20looks%20for%20increasingly%20rare%20acts%20of%20decency%20and%20sportsmanship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fugly-fans-and-honourable-sportspersons%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italy's%20Most-Wanted%20Mafia%20Boss%20Matteo%20Messina%20Denaro%20Dies%20At%2061%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EItalian%20Mafia%20boss%20Matteo%20Messina%20Denaro%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%20after%20spending%2030%20years%20on%20the%20run%20died%20on%20Monday%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66909616%5C%22%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0Denaro%20died%20at%20the%20San%20Salvatore%20hospital%20in%20L'Aquila%2C%20central%20Italy%2C%20where%20he%20had%20been%20treated%20for%20colon%20cancer.%C2%A0After%20his%20condition%20worsened%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20he%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20hospital%20from%20the%20maximum-security%20prison%20in%20central%20Italy%20where%20he%20was%20initially%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EL'Aquila%20mayor%20Pierluigi%20Biondi%20confirmed%20the%20mobster's%20death%20in%20a%20hospital%20%26quot%3Bfollowing%20a%20worsening%20of%20his%20illness%26quot%3B.%20His%20death%20%26quot%3Bputs%20the%20end%20to%20a%20story%20of%20violence%20and%20blood%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr.%20Biondi%20told%20the%20ANSA%20news%20agency.%C2%A0It%20was%20''the%20epilogue%20of%20an%20existence%20lived%20without%20remorse%20or%20repentance%2C%20a%20painful%20chapter%20of%20the%20recent%20history%20of%20our%20nation.''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDenaro%2C%20who%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20ordered%20dozens%20of%20Mafia-related%20murders%20for%20the%20Cosa%20Nostra%20crime%20group%2C%C2%A0was%20convicted%20for%20his%20role%20in%20planning%20the%201992%20murders%20of%20anti-mafia%20prosecutors%20Giovanni%20Falcone%20and%20Paolo%20Borsellino.%C2%A0He%20was%20also%20held%20responsible%20for%20bombings%20in%20Rome%2C%20Florence%20and%20Milan%20in%201993%20that%20killed%2010%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20six%20life%20sentences%20was%20for%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20subsequent%20murder%20of%20the%2012-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20Falcone%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDenaro%2C%20known%20as%20'The%20Last%20Godfather'%20by%20the%20Italian%20press%2C%20once%20boasted%20he%20could%20%26quot%3Bfill%20a%20cemetery%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20victims.%20He%20also%20oversaw%20racketeering%2C%20illegal%20waste%20dumping%2C%20money%20laundering%20and%20drug%20trafficking%20for%20the%20powerful%20Cosa%20Nostra%20organised%20crime%20syndicate.%C2%A0According%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fjan%2F16%2Fmatteo-messina-denaro-how-fast-