-india-2023%2Findia-vs-australia-dont-throw-your-wicket-away-virender-sehwag-advice-to-shubman-gill-despite-2nd-odi-ton-4421416%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Jawan%20Scene%20Because%20Of%20Which%20Atlee%20Got%20Calls%20From%20Hollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20receiving%20love%20from%20all%20quarters.%20Be%20it%20the%20songs%20or%20SRK's%20killer%20dialogues%2C%20the%20Atlee%20film%20is%20making%20all%20the%20right%20noises.%20%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20also%20become%20the%20fastest%20Hindi%20film%20to%20enter%20the%20Rs%20500-crore%20club.%20Now%2C%20it%20is%20eyeing%20to%20touch%20the%20Rs%201000-crore%20mark%20at%20the%20worldwide%20box%20office.%20The%20Jawan%20effect%2C%20did%20we%20hear%3F%20Now%2C%20Atlee%20has%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20approached%20by%20Hollywood%20directors%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%20film.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQgpYqC5798U%5C%22%3EFilm%20Companion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Atlee%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20who%20worked%20on%20our%20film%20%5B%3Ci%3EJawan%5D%3C%2Fi%3E%20were%20from%20Hollywood.%20Action%20director%20Spiro%20Razatos%20worked%20with%20us.%C2%A0%20So%2C%20Spiro%20and%20other%20great%20directors%20and%20technicians%20from%20Hollywood%20were%20at%20the%20same%20screening%20of%20%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E.%20And%2C%20Spiro%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20have%20done%20action%20in%20this%20film.'%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAtlee%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20particular%20action%20sequence%20loved%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20directors%20and%20technicians.%E2%80%9D%20FYI%3A%C2%A0%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20introduction%20scene.%20When%20his%20character%20Vikram%20Rathore%20finally%20wakes%20up%20and%20saves%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAtlee%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20they%20%5Bdirectors%20and%20technicians%5D%20asked%20Spiro%20who%20has%20done%20that%20scene%20where%20SRK%20is%20