0group%20Letko%20Brousseau%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%20and%20Imax%20Corporation%20have%20clashed%20over%20July%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20move%20to%20take%20private%20Imax%20China%2C%20which%20currently%20has%20a%20separate%20share%20listing%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20Letko%2C%20which%20owns%20some%201.7%25%20of%20Imax%20China%20shares%2C%20on%20Friday%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20vote%20against%20the%20proposal.%20It%20argues%20that%20the%20offer%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fimax-china-buyout-investor-1235734077%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fimax-china-buyout-investor-1235734077%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fimax-china-buyout-investor-1235734077%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Lakh%20Cameras%20And%20A%20Helipad%3A%20Hyderabad%20Police's%20New%20'War%20Room'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20one%20lakh%20cameras%2C%20a%20real-time%20traffic%20monitoring%20system%20and%20a%20helipad%20-%20the%20new%20war%20room%20at%20Hyderabad's%20Integrated%20Command%20and%20Control%20Centre%20(ICCC)%20resembles%20the%20US%20Pentagon's%20military%20command%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Home%20Minister%20Mahmood%20Ali%20today%20inaugurated%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20the%20country's%20most%20sophisticated%20ICCC%20at%20Hyderabad's%20police%20commissionerate%20headquarters.%20The%20room%20is%20equipped%20with%20state-of-the-art%20facilities%20that%20can%20enable%20all%20operations%20to%20be%20controlled%20centrally%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20helipad%20atop%20the%20building%20for%20choppers%20to%20take%20off%20and%20land%20during%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20advanced%20technologies%20including%20the%20mechanism%20to%20oversee%20a%20video%20surveillance%20system%20with%20over%20one%20lakh%20cameras%20installed%20across%20the%20city.%20A%20traffic%20monitoring%20system%20has%20been%20established%20in%20the%20war%20room%20that%20can%20track%20the%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20in%20Hyderabad%20in%20real-time%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20weather%20forecasting%20system%20has%20been%20set%20up%20that%20can%20provide%20early%20warnings%20of%20severe%20weather%20events.%20Taking%20disaster%20management%20to%20the%20next%20level%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20system%20that%20can%20coordinate%20the%20response%20to%20emergencies%20such%20as%20floods%2C%20fires%2C%20and%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20inaugurated%20the%20Hyderabad%20ICCC%20in%20August%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20spent%20around%20Rs%20500%20crore%20to%20construct%20the%20centre%2C%20which%20has%20five%20blocks.%20Tower%20A%20has%2019%20floors%2C%20including%20the%20ground%20floor.%20Tower%20B%20has%2015%20floors%20above%20the%20two%20basement%20floors.%20Tower%20C%20has%20three%20floors%2C%20including%20the%20auditorium%20ground%20floor.%20Tower%20D%20has%20two%20floors%2C%20including%20the%20ground%20floor.%20In%20Tower%20E%2C%20the%20CCC%20is%20located%20between%20the%20fourth%20and%20seventh%20floors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETower%20A%20is%20the%20tallest%20tower%2C%20with%2020%20floors.%20The%20DGP%20chamber%20is%20on%20the%20fourth%20floor%2C%20the%20Hyderabad%20Police%20Commissioner's%20chamber%20is%20on%20the%2018th%20floor%2C%20and%20other%20top-level%20officials'%20chambers%20are%20on%20the%20seventh%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695636660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fk65f9lio_hyderabad-police-war-room-_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhyderabad-news%2F1-lakh-cameras-and-a-helipad-hyderabad-polices-new-war-room-4421584%22%2C%2