2969651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%204%2C850%20ethnic%20Armenians%20have%20fled%20the%20territory%20of%20Nagorno-Karabakh%2C%20the%20Armenian%20government%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthousands-of-ethnic-armenians-flee-disputed-nagorno-karabakh-territory-after-azerbaijan-regains-control-12969651%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthousands-of-ethnic-armenians-flee-disputed-nagorno-karabakh-territory-after-azerbaijan-regains-control-12969651%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthousands-of-ethnic-armenians-flee-disputed-nagorno-karabakh-territory-after-azerbaijan-regains-control-12969651%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aadhaar%E2%80%99s%20Biometric%20Reliability%20in%20Hot%20and%20Humid%20Climate%20Is%20Questionable%3A%20Moody%E2%80%99s%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2FAadhaar.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ratings%20agency%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20Investors%20Service%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20security%20and%20privacy%20vulnerabilities%20in%20centralised%20identification%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20Aadhaar%20programme%2C%20saying%20that%20its%20biometric%20readability%20in%20hot%20and%20humid%20conditions%20is%20questionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%20administers%20Aadhaar%2C%20aiming%20to%20integrate%20marginalised%20groups%20and%20expand%20welfare%20benefits%20access%E2%80%A6The%20system%20often%20results%20in%20service%20denials%2C%20and%20the%20reliability%20of%20biometric%20technologies%2C%20especially%20for%20manual%20labourers%20in%20hot%2C%20humid%20climates%2C%20is%20questionable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20said%20in%20its%20report%20%E2%80%9CDecentralised%20Finance%20and%20Digital%20Assets%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Famid-indias-global-digital-public-infrastructure-pitch-moodys-questions-aadhaar-efficacy%2Farticle67342025.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ratings%20agency%20suggested%20that%20decentralised%20identity%20(DID)%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20digital%20wallets%2C%20based%20on%20blockchain%20technology%2C%20may%20be%20a%20better%20solution%2C%20as%20they%20give%20users%20more%20control%20over%20their%20private%20data%20and%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20online%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cited%20some%20examples%20of%20successful%20programmes%20in%20Catalonia%2C%20Azerbaijan%20and%20Estonia%20that%20have%20used%20blockchain-based%20systems%20to%20issue%20digital%20identities.%20%E2%80%9CEstonia%2C%20known%20for%20its%20fully%20digitalised%20public%20services%2C%20has%20embraced%20SSI%20%5BSelf-Sovereign%20Identity%5D%20to%20grant%20citizens%20complete%20control%20over%20their%20digital%20identities%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20centralised%20system%2C%20a%20single%20entity%20such%20as%20a%20bank%2C%20social%20media%20platform%20or%20government%20electoral%20roll%20controls%20and%20manages%20a%20user%E2%80%99s%20identifying%20credentials%20and%20their%20access%20to%20online%20resources.%20That%20entity%20can%20dispose%20of%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20identity%20data%20%E2%80%93%20name%2C%20address%20and%20Social%20Security%20number%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%93%20for%20internal%20or%20third-party%20profiling%20purposes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20such%20systems%20offer%20the%20least%20personal%20data%20control%20to%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20adoption%20of%20DID%20%E2%80%94%20where%20personal%20data%20is%20saved%20in%20a%20user%E2%80%99s%20digital%20wallet%20and%20identity%20verification%20takes%20place%20not%20via%20a%20single%2C%20centralised%20institution%20but%20on%20a%20decentralised%20digital%20ledger%20such%20as%20a%20blockchain%20%E2%80%94%20increases%20privacy%20and%20reduces%20the%20amount%20of%20personal%20information%20held%20by%20intermediaries%2C%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20noted.%20The%20DID%2C%20it%20said%2C%20can%20be%20stored%20and%20managed%20in%20a%20user%E2%80%99s%20portable%20and%20reusable%20digital%20wallet%2C%20rather%20than%20by%20a%20government%2C%20business%2C%20employer%2C%20or%20other%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20noted%20that%20decentralised%20IDs%20also%20pose%20some%20challenges.%20At%20a%20broader%20level%2C%20it%20warned%20that%20digital%20IDs%2C%20centralised%20or%20not%2C%20can%20cause%20problems%20at%20the%20social%20level%2C%20as%20they%20may%20strengthen%20group%20identities%20and%20political%20divides%2C%20particularly%20if%20offered%20by%20technology%20and%20social%20media%20companies%20with%20significant%20monopolistic%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsolidation%20of%20control%20within%20these%20entities%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20concentration%20of%20power%20over%20individual%20identities%2C%20shaping%20perceptions%20and%20interactions%20in%20the%20digital%20realm.%20Further%20polarisation%20of%20group%20identities%20and%20political%20affiliations%20would%20undermine%20the%20goal%20of%20a%20united%20and%20diverse%20digital%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695633557000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Faadhaars-biometric-reliability-in-hot-and-humid-climate-is-questionable-moodys%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ratings%20agency%20suggested%20that%20decentralised%20identity%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20digital%20wallets%2C%20based%20on%20blockchain%20technology%2C%20may%20be%20a%20better%20solution%2C%20as%20they%20give%20users%20more%20control%20over%20their%20private%20data%20and%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20online%20fraud.%22%2C%22aut