id%20or%20hinder%20his%20ambition%20to%20recapture%20power%20in%202024%3F%20Either%20way%2C%20Khalistan%2C%20which%20had%20died%20a%20rather%20quiet%20death%20by%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20century%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Punjab%20became%20exhausted%20after%20two%20decades%20of%20Sikh%20militancy%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20snowballing%20into%20a%20bigger%20issue%2C%20with%20international%20ramifications%20this%20time.%20Besides%2C%20within%20days%20of%20the%20Modi%20extravaganza%20in%20the%20name%20of%20G20%2C%20Trudeau%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20some%20of%20its%20shine%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Guru%20Nanak%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%20Sahib%2C%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%20also%20led%20the%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%20claims%20NIA%20which%20had%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest.%20In%20June%20this%20year%2C%20two%20men%20gunned%20down%20Nijjar%20outside%20the%20gurdwara.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20India%2C%20Canada%20has%20the%20largest%20Sikh%20population%20and%20Sikhs%20enjoy%20financial%20and%20political%20influence%20there.%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20led%20to%20widespread%20protests%20and%20street%20demonstrations%20by%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20who%20accused%20Indian%20intelligence%20of%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%2C%20who%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%20on%20October%208%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20told%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament%20on%20September%2018%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20up%20with%20Indian%20PM%20Modi%20allegations%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agencies%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20During%20the%20three-day%20meet%2C%20this%20rather%20sour%20note%20was%20kept%20away%20from%20the%20media.%20But%20Trudeau%20was%20forced%20to%20stay%20back%20for%2036%20hours%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20snag%20in%20his%20official%20plane%2C%20while%20he%20skipped%20the%20official%20banquet%20in%20honour%20of%20foreign%20delegates.%20He%20declined%20the%20offer%20of%20an%20Indian%20VIP%20plane%20to%20fly%20him%20home%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20release%20of%20his%20own%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-press-views-on-india-canada-row-nijjar-allegations%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Prickly%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%3A%20From%20a%20G20%20High%20to%20a%20Post-Canada%20Low%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20quite%20some%20time%20now%2C%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Sikh%20diaspora%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Canada%20but%20also%20in%20US%2C%20Britain%20and%20Australia%2C%20has%20been%20mobilising%20support%20for%20Khalistan.%20India%20has%20been%20raising%20this%20through%20official%20channels.%20But%20that%20has%20not%20helped%20much%2C%20insofar%20as%20this%20section%20of%20the%20diaspora%20has%20been%20holding%20protest%20demonstrations%20against%20Modi%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20majoritarianism%20and%20undermining%20the%20interests%20of%20all%20minorities%2C%20including%20Sikhs.%20They%20are%20throwing%20cold%20water%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20and%20his%20alma%20mater%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%2C%20attempts%20to%20project%20Sikhism%20not%20as%20a%20distinct%20religion%20but%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanth%3C%2Fem%3E%20(subsidiary)%20of%20Hindus%2C%20causing%20indignation%20and%20outrage%20among%20the%20Sikh%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20economic%20implications%20from%20the%20current%20standoff.%2016%20lakh%20people%20of%20Indian%20origin%20constitute%203%25%20of%20the%20Canadian%20population.%20Additionally%2C%202.3%20lakh%20Indian%20youth%20are%20studying%20and%20looking%20for%20work%20in%20Canada.%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20trade%20with%20Canada%20is%20worth%20US%2411.68%20billion%2C%20which%20includes%2030%25%20of%20the%20pulses%20imported%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal.%20Canadian%20pension%20funds%20have%20invested%20%2455%20billion%20in%20India.%20On%20September%2015%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20announced%20that%20it%20has%20put%20on%20hold%20the%20proposed%20October%20visit%20of%20a%20high-level%20trade%20delegation%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20concerns%20are%20political.%20The%20BJP%20presence%20in%20Punjab%20is%20negligible%2C%20except%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20or%20piggybacking%20on%20Bollywood%20stars%20%E2%80%95%20earlier%20Vinod%20Khanna%2C%20and%20now%20Sunny%20Deol.%20So%20the%20Nijjar%20controversy%20will%20not%20weaken%20an%20already%20weak%20BJP%20in%20Punjab%20much%20further.%20However%2C%20Modi%20might%20be%20looking%20at%20reaping%20the%20Khalistan%20harvest%20in%20adjoining%20territories%20like%20Jammu%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20appears%20a%20bit%20shaky.%20The%20BJP%20had%20labelled%20the%20year-long%20farmers%E2%80%99%20dharna%20on%20Delhi%20borders%20and%20their%20Republic%20Day%20entry%20into%20the%20national%20capital%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20conspiracy.%20But%20it%20had%20serious%20repercussions%20for%20Modi%2C%20who%20eventually%20capitulated%20on%20the%20three%20anti-farmers%20laws.%20Will%20the%20Khalistan%20issue%20win%20him%20political%20dividends%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695627950000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25130152%2FH20220429111448.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkhalistan-issue-aid-or-hinder-modi-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20BJP's%20presence%20in%20Punjab%20is%20negligible%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20may%20seek%20to%20reaping%20the%20Khalistan%20harvest%20in%20adjoining%20territories%20like%20Jammu%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%