-1235734004%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnetflix-beta-film-movistar-plus-wildside-morena-1235734004%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%206.6%20Million%20Frontline%20Jobs%20Created%20in%20FY23%20%E2%80%93%20A%20Decline%20of%2017.5%25%20From%20FY22%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F8391859530_aefbe96f68_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20number%20of%20frontline%20jobs%20created%20declined%2017.5%25%20year-on-year%20in%20fiscal%202022-23%20due%20to%20cautious%20hiring%20by%20companies%20amid%20macroeconomic%20headwinds%2C%20showed%20a%20report%20by%20frontline%20workforce%20management%20platform%20BetterPlace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%206.6%20million%20jobs%20were%20created%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%20as%20compared%20to%20eight%20million%20in%20FY22%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fjobs%2Fhr-policies-trends%2Ffrontline-job-creation-drops-17-5-per-cent-to-over-6-6-million-in-fy23-report%2Farticleshow%2F103914145.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20frontline%20jobs%20include%20customer%20facing%20roles%20such%20as%20call%20centre%20workers%2C%20delivery%20personnel%2C%20marketing%20executives%2C%20sales%20and%20business%20development%20executives%20and%20housekeeping%20staff%20among%20others.%20These%20jobs%20are%20critical%20because%20the%20employees%20in%20these%20roles%20are%20often%20the%20face%20of%20the%20company.%20Their%20interactions%20with%20customers%20can%20significantly%20impact%20a%20company%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20and%20customer%20satisfaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20comes%20after%20companies%20went%20on%20a%20hiring%20spree%20after%20in%20FY22%20when%20businesses%20reopened%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2