e%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Golden%20Langur%20or%20%3Cem%3ESonali%20Bandor.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20My%20namesake%20and%20I%20have%20since%20then%20shared%20a%20special%20bond%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20lovingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20of%20her%20favourite%20workplaces%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20fortunate%20to%20have%20served%20at%20Manas%20National%20Park%20with%20its%20sheer%20natural%20beauty%20and%20unique%20conservation%20and%20governance%20models.%20It%20taught%20me%20that%20there%20are%20many%20sides%20to%20a%20coin%20and%20one%20must%20appreciate%20history%20to%20become%20an%20effective%20administrator.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESonali%20also%20served%20a%20tenure%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Zoo%20in%20Delhi%20before%20she%20accepted%20the%20role%20at%20Kaziranga.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20Kaziranga%20her%20%3Cem%3EKarma%20Bhoomi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land%20of%20action)%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshe%20fondly%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20the%20state%20at%20Kaziranga%20as%20a%20probationary%20trainee.%20At%20that%20time%20I%20was%2020%20years%20younger%20and%2020%20kg%20lighter!%20So%20when%20a%20rhino%20chased%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20courage%20and%20strength%20to%20climb%20a%20tree!%20I%20dread%20what%20will%20happen%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20a%20range%20of%20vital%20tasks%2C%20from%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%2C%20to%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20She%20also%20engages%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20delving%20into%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215138%2Fsustainable-e-commerce-karnival-shopping-online-eco-friendly-homegrown-products-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3