C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20released%20a%20contact-route%20map%20to%20help%20one%20establish%20connections.%20They%20have%20found%20950%20people%20who%20were%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20first%20five%20patients%20and%20213%20have%20been%20marked%20as%20high-risk.%20Close%20contacts%20are%20being%20quarantined%2C%20while%20containment%20zones%20have%20been%20made%20and%20fever%20cases%20are%20being%20tested%20for%20Nipah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20questions%20are%20arising%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304986%2Fkerala-aluva-seed-farm-first-in-india-to-become-carbon-neutral%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20it%20is%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20these%20cases%20are%20first%20diagnosed.%20Dr%20Kumar%20attributes%20this%20to%20the%20excellent%20healthcare%20surveillance%20system%20in%20the%20state%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20evaluating%20rare%20viruses%20thanks%20to%20our%20quick%20diagnosis.%20We%20have%20a%20great%20public%20healthcare%20system.%20We%20contain%20diseases%20fast%20due%20to%20swift%20action%20in%20any%20unusual%20fever%20cases.%20Private%20clinicians%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20government%20health%20department%20which%20prevents%20the%20disease%20from%20spreading%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694789032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Anoop%20Kumar%20AS%2C%20critical%20care%20specialist%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20teams%20that%20were%20able%20to%20diagnose%20Nipah%20virus%20with%20their%20quick%20thinking%20and%20swift%20actio